    "Here, we collect available public datasets for educational data mining and provide a detailed description for each dataset.",
    "We summarize the characteristics of each dataset to facilitate researchers in efficient selection of the dataset that is applicable to their current research.",
    "• Research direction categorization.",
    "We summarize existing research directions in student cognitive modeling including detailed description, representative papers, and commonly used datasets of each research direction.",
    "This enables researchers to swiftly comprehend the student cognitive modeling."
